{"tid":1869190,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大實驗室測試   iPhone 11 Pro 輻射超標 137%","createTime":"2020-02-08T04:54:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T05:39:08.000Z","uid":1886,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2f2eea2584e97cdd162d1fb9552f6ff9a4d336ab","tid":1869190,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/215125/1/1/142848/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4544%2F215125%2F1%2F1%2F142848%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=00f6b9c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/215125/1/1/142848/</a><br />\n<br />\niPhone 11 Pro 自從去年年底上市後，一直深受消費者歡迎，不過日前加拿大一間獨立實驗室發表的報告，則可能令對健康相當緊張的消費者打退堂鼓。專門進行電磁波測試的 RF Exposure Lab 對 iPhone 11 Pro 測試，結果輻射量超出法定數值。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2020-02/05/215125/uniqlo_1_7461db3b89e35b4b9f9b580a2fd232bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2020-02%2F05%2F215125%2Funiqlo_1_7461db3b89e35b4b9f9b580a2fd232bb.jpg&h=83d53b99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據 RF Exposure Lab 的測試結果，iPhone 11 Pro 的 SAR 值（即 Specific Absorption Rate）達 3.8W/Kg，超過了美國聯邦通訊委員會 1.6W/Kg 的法定上限。SAR 是用作密實流動通訊產品中電磁波所產生的能量，對人體影響的衡量數據。相對寬鬆的歐盟標準是 2.0W/Kg，但 iPhone 11 Pro 在 RF Exposure Lab 的測試中仍然超標。"},{"pid":"d96f80145c8439dd68884a49645f91fcbd985b9e","tid":1869190,"uid":57308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"用家問題"},{"pid":"cacca8f1cbb756d79397eff55cb02b0c064862be","tid":1869190,"uid":9387,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"輻射高可以消毒<br />\niPhone user又贏"},{"pid":"211f8848384b732a1aebb1bcd3dd6e071ec75878","tid":1869190,"uid":30674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:06:11.000Z","msg":"係咪防到WARS? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b5732ed67041912805e29a4d14344177d854a6","tid":1869190,"uid":9387,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"211f8848384b732a1aebb1bcd3dd6e071ec75878","tid":1869190,"uid":30674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:06:11.000Z","msg":"係咪防到WARS? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"買iPhone 送輻射防護罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Tim Cook佛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4eecbc55429f02cc47607a9e958f60e86db0b94","tid":1869190,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:28:50.000Z","msg":"idog : an 狗收皮啦，an 機仲多幅射"},{"pid":"acc95082ea4286a17e66917154625eeb3e0e075e","tid":1869190,"uid":210638,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:29:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾iphone<br />\n利申11"},{"pid":"aa364973f7967870518fbffbfa7ce0fcedbcc4d4","tid":1869190,"uid":204722,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:38:22.000Z","msg":"用intel晶片收得差所以加大power補償"},{"pid":"fac719f2c1c70b447af60507a596ef768d876e28","tid":1869190,"uid":52417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:42:07.000Z","msg":"仲用緊X<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f21a83eca9e0078662de951f1a2bf79007823b","tid":1869190,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:32:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69c293294d95ee3fc1b0a705d184d4de042f294f","tid":1869190,"uid":3223,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:14:29.000Z","msg":"Non ionising frequency 好似唔會對人體有影響<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等physics 人答<br />\n<br />\n利申apple fan"},{"pid":"7124c8080ab6d9e8aa725232744b0aaef4d708c7","tid":1869190,"uid":55552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T19:4